name: Kusamon: The last starter
description:
Why wasn't I chosen and got left alone?

This is the question plantisaur asks himself and maybe you will find the reason out.

This game was made for the Weeklly Game Jam 149 with the theme Last One Left.

Please leave feedback down below. 

And to play the game from the beginning again press the delete key and then reload the site/ reopen the game.
